HEADWORD: overachiever
<hw>overachiever</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A student who
attains higher standards than expected based on the IQ score.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A person whose achievements exceed what was expected
based on his/her background, education, or mental ability.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Overact</ent>⟦br⟧
